      <section id="id1165507056029">
        <title>To understand and use nouns which do not have plurals [LO 6.4.2]</title>
        <para id="id1165513589602">Some words, however, don’t have a plural form at all, for example:</para>
        <para id="id1165500030068">tourism, space, exploitation, respect, pollution (as used in this module)</para>
        <para id="id1165515483184">See if you can find any other nouns that don’t have a plural form.</para>
      </section>
